  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">draw_rectangle_colour(50, 50, 200, 200, c_black, c_white, c_black, c_white, false);
</code></pre>
  This would draw a filled-in square with a smooth black/white gradient between the corners.
